That's a rare one.  Most of those pictures were taken in Yamanashi prefecture in the late '90's.  The breakfast photo was at Hagihara-sensei's brother's inn in Enzan.  The other guy is Joe Bott who is also from the LA area and is a very long time collector.
  Breakfast in his pajamas has to be my favorite shot...
